&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I&rsquo;m not sure what that question is.&nbsp; Why would I do that --<br />
&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; We'll check on that and get back to you.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Robert, has the press office or anyone here at the White House put the freeze on the Agriculture Department in terms of taking questions from reporters?&nbsp; It&rsquo;s been our experience in the past 24 hours or so that they are not being responsive.<br />
