&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; Look, obviously there is -- I&rsquo;d lead the Greek G.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If we can get back to Secretary Vilsack&rsquo;s role in all of this.&nbsp; My understanding from the timeline that you just suggested here and that other White House officials have said was that the White House was informed but not consulted about his decision to fire her.<br />
