&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; You know this, I know this, I think everybody knows this.&nbsp; This was -- race has been a topic of discussion for a long, long time in this country.&nbsp; We -- a war was fought about it.&nbsp; A movement to gain equal and civil rights was had to rectify injustice.&nbsp; And it continues to be something that we will discuss for quite sometime.&nbsp; Again, I think this is -- this just continues many of those discussions.<br />
